## v1.0.0 (2026-05-18) — Merge of 14 skills

**Changed by:** Skill-merge swarm (Phase B Wave 1, M5 / #1779)
**Verification:** verified-local

### What changed

Consolidated 14 CI-failure-triage and diagnosis skills into a single canonical skill.

