## Superseded from modular-6433-vs-6413-failure-triage

```yaml
name: modular-6433-vs-6413-failure-triage
description: "Distinguish modular#6433 (OOM, fixed) from modular#6413 (libKGEN JIT crash, open) when verifying upstream fixes."
category: ci-cd
date: 2026-05-11
version: "1.0.0"
verification: verified-ci
```

Bash triage script + decision matrix mapping log signature to action. OOM keywords = #6433; libKGENCompilerRTShared.so+0x = #6413. Exit code 137 is NOT a discriminator — both crash types can produce it. Correctly classified all 7 failed jobs on ProjectOdyssey PR #5381 as #6413 (no revert needed).

