## Superseded from ci-mojo-podman-root-cause-fixes

```yaml
name: ci-mojo-podman-root-cause-fixes
description: "Fix four distinct CI root-cause classes: mkdocs --strict broken relative links, Podman container PermissionError, Mojo ASAN builds, Mojo circular imports."
category: ci-cd
date: 2026-03-28
version: "1.0.0"
```

Four CI failure root causes in Mojo/Podman projects: (1) mkdocs strict broken relative links — path exits docs tree; (2) Podman PermissionError — write to /tmp inside container then podman cp; (3) Mojo ASAN via justfile + libasan8; (4) circular imports fixed by extracting shared constants to zero-dependency leaf module. Verified on ProjectOdyssey PR #5178.

