## Superseded from ci-cd-broken-main-parallel-fix-wave

```yaml
name: ci-cd-broken-main-parallel-fix-wave
description: "Triage and fix broken CI/main across multiple repos simultaneously using Agamemnon task registry + parallel myrmidon fix agents."
category: ci-cd
date: 2026-05-17
version: "1.5.0"
verification: verified-ci
history: ci-cd-broken-main-parallel-fix-wave.history
```

Full ecosystem broken-main triage pattern: org-wide CI sweep, transient vs reproducible triage, Agamemnon task registration, agent-tier selection (Haiku for known-fix, Sonnet for unknown root cause). 13 known fix patterns documented. Critical: check main BEFORE rebasing downstream PRs. Identical failure across N unrelated PRs = broken-main even for lint failures. Verified across 14 HomericIntelligence repos, multiple sessions 2026-04-24 through 2026-05-18.

