## Superseded from symbolicate-mojo-cores-inside-container

```yaml
name: symbolicate-mojo-cores-inside-container
description: "Post-mortem symbolication of Mojo JIT crash cores must run INSIDE the pixi container via podman compose exec."
category: ci-cd
date: 2026-05-12
version: "1.0.0"
verification: verified-ci
```

Symbolication of captured Mojo JIT crash cores must run inside the container because the mojo binary and pixi env are only visible in the container's mount namespace. Key: heredoc quoting — host-expanded variables bare, container-expanded with single backslash, gdb -ex strings with three backslashes. Always emit info all-registers (surfaces zmm/k-register AVX-512 state). Identified 6 distinct AVX-512 instruction sites across 10+ symbolicated cores confirming ISA-feature-mismatch bug (modular/modular#6413). Verified on ProjectOdyssey PR #5399.

