## Superseded from ci-cd-pixi-lock-stale-multi-pr-triage

```yaml
name: ci-cd-pixi-lock-stale-multi-pr-triage
description: "Use when multiple PR branches failing CI with 'lock-file not up-to-date' or pixi.lock stale errors."
category: ci-cd
date: 2026-04-24
version: "1.0.0"
verification: verified-local
```

Cross-repo CI triage and stale pixi.lock remediation: bulk PR status query, SHA mismatch detection, gh run rerun --failed (empty commits don't reliably trigger CI with concurrency cancel-in-progress). Platform-specific bats-core deps, LRU-cached FastAPI settings in tests, Protocol method missing. Verified across 7 repos / 42 open PRs.

