## Superseded from ci-cd-required-context-never-posts-pr-blocked

```yaml
name: ci-cd-required-context-never-posts-pr-blocked
description: "Diagnose a PR with mergeStateStatus BLOCKED but zero failing checks."
category: ci-cd
date: 2026-05-15
version: "1.0.0"
verification: verified-ci
```

Two mechanisms for BLOCKED PR with 0 FAILUREs: (1) workflow paths: filter excludes PR's files so workflow never triggers; (2) whole-job if: skip on event type shows as MISSING to branch protection (not success). Diagnosis: diff required-vs-present contexts via protection API + statusCheckRollup. Do NOT admin-merge as fix — it's systemic. Verified on ProjectOdyssey PR #5382 → fixed in PRs #5406/#5407.

