## Superseded from ci-cd-github-api-rate-limit-ci-monitoring

```yaml
name: ci-cd-github-api-rate-limit-ci-monitoring
description: "Avoid and recover from GitHub API rate limit exhaustion (5000/hr) during intensive CI diagnostic loops."
category: ci-cd
date: 2026-04-24
version: "1.0.0"
verification: verified-local
```

Rate limit budget management for batch CI investigations: always check before starting (gh api rate_limit), prefer bulk endpoints (gh pr list --json over per-PR calls), gate log fetching (stop at remaining < 500), calculate exact reset time for sleep. Observed exhaustion in under 2 hours on AchaeanFleet 13-PR session.

